        <h2>3.3 Common Symptoms</h2>

        <p>
            Some of the more common symptoms of MS will now be defined and described in more detail. 
            Different strategies that an MS Nurse might use to manage these symptoms will be discussed 
            in Module 4 and Module 5.<br />
